Package: BasicPipe4mArrays
Type: Package
Title: Functions to crete and run simple-to-complex microarray analysis pipeline
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Alex Sanchez, Josep Lluis Mosquera, Israel Ortega, Ferran Brianso, Ricardo Gonzalo, Mercedes Guerrero
Maintainer: Alex Sanchez <alex.sanchez@vhir.org>
Description: This package is intended to create and run microarray data analysis projects using a two steps approach: 
    (1) The project is defined by setting an extensive set of parameters
    (2) The project is run based on those parameters in a completely automatic way.
Imports: affy, oligo, annotate, AnnotationDbi, GO.db, reactome.db, GOstats, gplots, rgl, SortableHTMLTables, VennDiagram, grDevices, grid, limma, stats, org.Hs.eg.db, BiocParallel
License: GPL 2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
